1229
01:35:03,950 --> 01:35:07,230
Even if he could, which he can't.

1230
01:35:07,230 --> 01:35:11,950
But that's not true, Richard,
you can, you have. I just love it.

1231
01:35:11,950 --> 01:35:13,234
No, you don't.

1232
01:35:13,390 --> 01:35:15,274
It's lousy.

1233
01:35:17,710 --> 01:35:20,108
In any case, the problem is, ...

1234
01:35:22,830 --> 01:35:25,950
