1239
01:35:36,350 --> 01:35:38,492
relatively handsome stranger.

1240
01:35:39,390 --> 01:35:41,274
Me.

1241
01:35:41,310 --> 01:35:46,590
Smooth as silk with
a highly practised line of chatter,

1242
01:35:46,590 --> 01:35:51,790
specifically designed to knock
relatively unsophisticated chicks

1243
01:35:51,790 --> 01:35:56,159
like you, Miss Simpson,
right on their ears.

1244
01:35:56,750 --> 01:35:59,662
Which I'm terribly afraid
I have done.

1245
01:36:01,790 --> 01:36:07,230
Well, ... if it's the last
decent thing I do in this world,

1246
01:36:07,230 --> 01:36:10,056
and it very well may be,

1247
01:36:10,430 --> 01:36:12,314
I'm going to fix that.

1248
01:36:13,950 --> 01:36:16,006
I'm going to send you packing,

1249
01:36:16,030 --> 01:36:17,914
Miss Simpson.

1250
01:36:19,230 --> 01:36:21,886
Before I cause you serious...

1251
01:36:23,710 --> 01:36:26,708
..and irrevocable harm.

1252
01:36:27,950 --> 01:36:30,006
You want the truth?

1253
01:36:31,150 --> 01:36:33,206
Of course you don't.

1254
01:36:35,390 --> 01:36:37,874
I'll give it to you anyway.

1255
01:36:38,990 --> 01:36:42,750
I do not give one damn
about anything,

1256
01:36:42,750 --> 01:36:45,870
certainly not my work,
as you so touchingly

1257
