and ingenuously call it.

1258
01:36:51,150 --> 01:36:53,710
Well, that's not true.

1259
01:36:53,710 --> 01:36:57,908
There is something I care about.
Money.

1260
01:36:58,190 --> 01:37:00,931
And good whisky.

1261
01:37:01,550 --> 01:37:04,030
I am, as you've probably noticed,

1262
01:37:04,030 --> 01:37:05,914
rather fond of that.

1263
01:37:10,590 --> 01:37:12,560
But my work?

1264
01:37:13,790 --> 01:37:15,502
That's a hideous little something

1265
01:37:15,550 --> 01:37:18,430
that must occur
five days out of the year

1266
01:37:18,430 --> 01:37:21,470
so I can spend the other 360

1267
01:37:21,470 --> 01:37:24,430
in the manner
to which I have become -

1268
01:37:24,430 --> 01:37:28,628
and fully intend to remain -
accustomed.

